snippet.title: Doctor Kids | Hospital Game for Kids
snippet.description:
Preview of "Doctor Kids" by Pilcom. With the help of this educational game you can be a doctor and treat kids in a children's hospital. You can make them healthy again and put a smile back on their faces. Kids are counting on you!

➔ App Download (Apple App Store): https://goo.gl/QCYJY9
➔ App Download (Google Play App Store): https://goo.gl/Lm4hsr
➔ Subscribe our YouTube channel: http://goo.gl/ok7zCw
➔ Go to our Website: http://www.greatapps4kids.com

Children are coming to the clinic, injured or suffering from various diseases, and they need your help to get better. Once you appoint the little patients to the right doctor’s office, you can have fun playing interactive minigames and treat kids in no time.

Game presents various injuries and different kinds of doctors and treatments, with many colorful objects to match patients’ characteristics. Every doctor’s office includes a unique minigame to make treatment even more fun. And don’t forget about the ambulance car that is always in a hurry.

Within this game, you can do the following:
Appoint your patients to the dentist to brush and fix their broken teeth.
Diagnose and vaccinate patients to heal them from strange diseases.
Make an eye examination test to improve kids’ eyesight.
Use a microscope to make some lab tests and eliminate viruses.
Use the X-ray machine to locate fractures and heal broken bones.
Drive an ambulance car and give first aid to patients.

This game will keep your children occupied for hours and will also help them overcome the fear of visiting the doctor’s office.

Features:
• kids friendly content (without violence, zombies or scares)
• beautiful high quality HD graphics
• intuitive, easy to use user interface
• infinite gameplay with numerous combinations
• many different patients in various clothes
• game offers 6 unique doctor’s offices: dental care, eye check, vaccination, lab test and X-ray, ambulance car with emergency room (ER doctor)
• includes 6 thematic minigames
• tons of colorful plasters, bandages, braces, glasses and syrup flavours

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.playkids.crazy.fun.kids.ear.doctor

On his way back from school, John was suffering from pain in ear. Mommy was very worried and decided to called the kids ENT specialist at kid’s clinic to prepare for an ER emergency ENT treatment till John reaches hospital in an ambulance. Get your doctor tools and prepare for a dental treatment so that John recovers quickly. All you have to do is to examine and treat all your patients very carefully. Enjoy the thrill of being an ENT doctor to cure all kids coming to your clinic and bringing them back from trauma. Be careful, don’t get the bones and face skin damaged. There are some problems with crazy kids ears. Could you please give crazy kids ear surgery and cure them all use medical tools to stretch ears wide open, tweeze ear hairs, remove bugs and discover all kinds of surprises in crazy kids ears! You can even use the laser beam to burn ear infections!

* choose from different instruments to treat the patient
* real life medical tools like syringes, ear spray and more
* Remove wax with a cotton bud
* remove hairs in the ear
* Pluck out the germs

* find the bacteria and eliminate them by using disinfectant spray
* use the laser beam to burn infections

snippet.title: Amazing Car Wash For Girls - Google Play Android Kids Game from McPeppergames
snippet.description:
The new Car Wash game for kids from McPeppergames aims mainly at little girls age 2 to 9, featuring a lot of "girly" cars, pink car wash action tools combined with a big portion of fun.

What makes this game unique are the tons of available action tools which can be cross combined to discover a lot of cool actions. All tools are available from the beginning and don't have to be used in a row. The actions can be stopped at all time and the tool bar can be moved outside of the screen, so only the car stays visible on the display. And if this is not enough the kids can collect stars by washing the cars and then "spend" the stars for cool "dirt" actions to make the cars dirty in creative ways.

Beware! There even is a flying fire breathing dragon in the game! :)

The app is now available for Android on Google Play.
